@remark ==================================================================
@Node _HISTORY                                                   "History"
@toc Main

@{fg highlight}History@{fg text}

V1.0  14-Feb-1997

 - Initial release

V1.1  03-Apr-1997

 - changed: Case insensitive pattern selection
 - changed: User variables moved from '*.cfg' to '*.var'
 - added  : Default output filename definable in user settings
 - added  : Onlinehelp for user configurations '*.hlp'
 - added  : '*.info' Icon for generated output file
 - added  : Configuration 'FTP-Mail script for YAM'
 - added  : Configuration 'BatchWindow file for AmFTP'
 - updated: Configuration 'Download script for MountFTP'
 - updated: Configuration 'Download script for AmFTP'

V1.2  17-Apr-1997

 - added  : Configurable 'Process output after save'
 - added  : Plugin for MailManager
 - changed: GUI button layout
 - changed: Onlinehelp now scrollable
 - fixed  : Error if no '*.info' available

V1.3  09-Jul-1997

 - added  : Virtual (scrollable) group at settings dialog
 - changed: ',' will be translated to ';' due to MUIRexx flaw

V1.4  18-Jul-1997

 - added  : 'Save as' mode can be saved as global setting
 - added  : 'Quit after save' can be saved as global setting
 - changed: Filerequester is suppressed at execute mode 'Always'

V1.5  04-Sep-1997

 - added  : File and kByte counters
 - added  : Configuration 'HTML download page'
 - added  : Import script support
 - added  : Import from YAM
 - added  : Import from Thor
 - added  : Import from IntuiNews
 - added  : Plugin for Thor
 - added  : Plugin for IntuiNews
 - added  : 'Import from' mode can be saved as global setting
 - added  : Popup menu for lists
 - changed: Improved pattern selection speed
 - changed: Names of Plugin scripts
 - fixed  : Reselection of *.readme checkmark
 - fixed  : Plugin YAM - Error without a selected mail

V1.6  16-Nov-1997

 - added  : Excluding of non-interest directories via AminetFilter
 - added  : Support of AmiNet index files with 'Age' column
 - added  : Support of 'Most Downloaded' in 'Weekly Recent Mails'
 - added  : Support of 'Top Rated'       in 'Weekly Recent Mails'
 - added  : PopUp menu item 'Sort by file'
 - added  : Icon examples for output files
 - updated: Default Icons for output files

V1.7  14-Mar-1998

 - added  : Output configuration 'AmigaGuide'
 - added  : Output configuration 'Spreadsheet CSV'
 - added  : Output configuration 'Thor FTP-Mail'
 - added  : Output configuration 'UMS FTP-Mail'
 - added  : Importer 'OnlineSearch' - Direct search on AmiNet
 - added  : New entry variables for fixed width output
 - fixed  : Error at batchmode settings window without variables
 - fixed  : Error at filerequester without an initial drawer
 - fixed  : Some minor internal bug fixes
 - fixed  : Now supports empty batchmode variables
 - updated: YAM Importer/Plugin marks imported mail as readed
 - updated: Alphabetic sort of batchmodes
 - changed: Layout of batchmode settings window
@EndNode
